Remember Me Girl group VARIOUS introduces their new member Dongah By beansss 4 minutes ago 389 40 0 0 Google+ Girl group VARIOUS has recruited a new member! SEE ALSO: Woollim Boys reveal individual teaser images of Jang Jun and Young Taek for 2nd 'W Project' VARIOUS, who debuted last April as a group of 5, suffered from a member loss when Hyebin left the group due to health issues. They will now return as a group of 5 with their brand new member Dongah , whose teaser image shows off her lovely, cute charms with a flower in her hair, parted in two pigtails. The group will also be making a comeback this February 15 with their 2nd digital single, " Barbie Girl ". What do you think of VARIOUS's new member Dongah?
